jeSbO dNWPds pf-186_">Oversee go-to-market plans for HydroPeptide.com and partner .com sites, leveraging best-in-class customer launch strategies for key eCommerce/retail partners</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-187_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-189_">Build and maintain internal activation calendar, product assortment recommendations and cross selling opportunities</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-190_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-192_">Drive the execution of ecommerce activations, partnering with creative, brand and marketing</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-193_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-195_">Build and manage sales forecasts by channel. Partner with analyst to track weekly performance</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-196_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-198_">Collaborate with Product Development to brainstorm and develop .com exclusive products, bundles and kits</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-199_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-201_">Partner with Supply Chain to ensure forecasts are in line with go to market plans and financial forecasts</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-202_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-204_">Drive online revenue growth in partnership with Acquisition and Retention teams; identify strategies that will drive short term and long term growth</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-205_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-207_">Leverage data to understand who our HP.com customer is and develop strategies to increase conversion</span></li></ul><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jvvksu EHytM pf-208_ TT-Norms-Normal"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-210_"><span style="font-style: italic;">Site</span></span></h4><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:16px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-itWPBs iHZleA pf-211_ TT-Norms-Normal"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-212_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-214_">Lead the development of the overall eCommerce experience roadmap, ensuring alignment to company objectives and strategy</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-215_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-217_">Own the prioritization, planning, and ultimate implementation of the features, functionality, and capabilities needed to support the roadmap</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-218_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-220_">Understand the customer journey and oversee the design and infrastructure of the website, working closely with our developer and web producer to create a frictionless experience</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-221_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-223_">Strategize and implement new site experiences</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-224_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-226_">Maximize online conversion by developing effective customer journeys, multi-device strategies and optimizing site performance</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-227_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-229_">In partnership with Analyst, create and build tracking and conversion funnels and focus on improving business metrics to optimize the CX and enhance conversion</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-230_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-232_">Manage site merchandising and new product launches on .com with support from Web Producer</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-233_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-235_">Implement, launch and test new website functionality</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-236_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-238_">Drive content strategy with SEO in mind, in effort to grow organic rankings</span></li></ul><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jvvksu EHytM pf-239_ TT-Norms-Normal"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-241_"><span style="font-style: italic;">Strategy and Leadership</span></span></h4><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:16px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-itWPBs iHZleA pf-242_ TT-Norms-Normal"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-243_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-245_">Play a strategic role as a proactive subject matter expert to the leadership team on technology and investment required to support customer experience</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-246_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-248_">Passionate about data-driven decision making, with a strong commercial instinct and obsession with the customer experience, informing creative, brand and site decisions</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-249_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-251_">Ability to lead both directly and indirectly with oversight of direct reports and external partners and agencies including a web producer, developer and UX designer</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-252_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-254_">Partner with teammates to brainstorm white space opportunities and channel execution</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-255_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-257_">Launch new international markets and .com partners</span></li></ul></div></div><