tomer experience (Both DTC and B2B) and passionate about increasing customer lifetime value</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-284_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-286_">Strong bias for action with ability to translate data into actionable insights</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-dcgwPl ixgdqM pf-287_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-289_">Team player, ability to serve as player/coach when needed and roll up sleeves to get the job done</span></li></ul></div></div></div><a href="mailto:careers@hydropeptide.com?subject=Sr.%20Manager,%20Ecommerce%20Position" data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-gIBqdA dpOKeD pf-290_ TT-Norms-Normal"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-292_">APPLY</span></a></div></div></div><p class="sc-hGnimi ljiQdr pf-293_ TT-Norms-Normal" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-295_">Please check back for future opportunities.</span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:5;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bGaVxB jzqjUH pf-296_"><p class="sc-hGnimi ljiQdr pf-297_ TT-Norms-Normal" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjeSbO dNWPds pf-299_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">HydroPeptide</span> is a rapidly growing high-end skincare company with a focus on both Direct to Consumer and salon &amp; spa wholesale business.We pride ourselves on clean ingredients and clinical results. We make skincare fun through leading-edge science, innovative technologies and luxury sensory experiences. Our brand is known for results-driven, efficacious products and professional treatments that make you look and feel amazing. <br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br>Perks and benefits of working here include:</span> flexible schedules, comprehensive insurance benefits, store discounts,  generous paid time off and more. We welcome employees and candidates with diverse b